data.description: LOVE WHERE YOU LIVE! Modern styled end unit 3 story townhome in popular Benns Grant near quaint Smithfield. Like New, Built 2021, 4 BR/ 3.5 baths. First floor Bedroom w/ Full bath great for guests or a home office. Turn up the music & entertain in your gourmet kitchen with spacious island; lots of seating area & built-in beverage bar & storage hutch; large pantry; recessed & pendent lighting plus natural lighting; ceiling fans. Granite countertops accent white cabinets, stainless appliances. Morning room/dining leads to balcony. Spacious living area w/ LVP flooring.  Upper level includes 2 additional guest rooms & guest Bath. Primary bedroom features tray ceiling, walk-in closet & ensuite w/ tiled shower, soaking tub, dual basin vanity. 2 car rear-entry garage. Community Amenities invite fun & relaxation at the resort styled pool, clubhouse, playgrounds, walking path, lakes. Convenient to schools, shopping, restaurants and bases. Some images edited by Artificial Intelligence.
